snippet.title: Jane's Combat Simulations: Longbow Anthology (1998) - Teaser
snippet.description:
Official trailer for Jane's Combat Simulations: Longbow Anthology by ORIGIN Systems.

Previously removed from YouTube after the account owner threw in the towel for no apparent reason (not DMCAs). Of course, re-encoding made the quality dip further.
